हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा।

show.description:
A hardened soldier takes on his toughest mission yet—guarding a powerful CEO from lurking shadows. As corporate conspiracies unravel, every bullet and betrayal tests his loyalty and strength.
But in the heart of chaos, an unexpected love becomes both his greatest risk and his only refuge.
